                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.602/29: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Latvia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Coleman</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-01-16T16:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 16, 1928—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>6. Your telegram No. 8, dated January 12, 4 p.m. You may accept proposed
                    paragraph 3 of protocol with insertion of reference to article 19 in text
                    contained in Foreign Office memorandum of March 5, 1927, which was enclosed with
                    Legation’s despatch No. 4408 of March 21, 1927.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Olds</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
